      "page_content": "{'column_name': 'include_in_recommendations', 'table_name': 'CustomBaseImageAttributes', 'type': 'boolean', 'description': 'Indicates whether the custom base image should be recommended for use as an upgrade.', 'properties': {'description': 'Whether this image should be recommended as a base image upgrade. \\nIf set to true, this image could be shown as a base image upgrade to other projects.\\nIf set to false this image will never be recommended as an upgrade.\\n', 'business_significance': 'This boolean flag determines the visibility of the image in upgrade recommendations, impacting user decisions on image selection.'}}",
